The paper discusses techniques for learning probabilistic programs, which involves probabilistic programming languages and Markov chain Monte Carlo inference techniques. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY).
